testcase.title: Verify predictions are downloaded as PPT for different input search

I verify 'Prediction' button is displayed on page 'Results'

I select the 'Select all Drugs' checkbox in Intermediate page

steps.title: I verify all the drugs are being selected in Intermediate page

I select the 'Select all Drugs' checkbox in Prediction page

substeps.message: Drugs are  selected in Prediction screen

I click on PowerPoint format to download
